'''tadyant n inğamina''' n15 yunyu 2015  teḍra-d deg uberrem n [[buku haram]] d afrid amezzwaru ara tissin [[Tamanaɣt|tmanaɣt]] [[Ččad|n Ččad]] tadyant tarebrabt s tenɣimant .

== tigawin ==
tanezzayt n 15 yunyu 2015 , tamdint n [[Nǧamena]], tamannaɣt n [[Ččad]] , tuki-d ɣef xilla n teddyanin tirebrabin s tenɣimant . Di tazwara rran ɣer tenmehla n laman tazayezt  d uxxam n yimsulta alemmas anda i ṭṭerḍqen sin n yikamikazen . ula d aɣerbaz n yimsulta rran ɣur-s ardekkal  d takerrust i yenher yiwen n ukamikaz yekcem yis s abraḥ yeṭṭerḍeq ula d netta muten xilla n medden imiren . terna-d tsunayt nniḑen ula d nettat teṭṭerḍeqsdat n tewwurt n uɣerbaz mi rewwlen yinelmaden  mmuten azal n 38 n yimdanen jerḥen azal n 101 .

== Anegmi ==
ardekal tadyant ,adabu n [[Ččad]] nnan-d zik belli dBoko Haram,, tarbaɛt n l ğihad lukud ttnaɣen yiserdasen n tmurt n [[Ččad]] tsekcem-d iman-is di [[Nijirya]] daɣen di tmurt n  [[Kamirun|kamiroun]] di yennayer [[2015]]. [[8 yulyu]] , nnan-d yimḍebbren n « uwanek ineslem, agezdu n Tefriqt n umalu » belli d tidet d nutni i g-xedmen annecta , « awanek ineslem, agezdu n Tefriqt n umalu »  d isem amaynut unsin n Buku Ḥaram mi dduklen d '[[Awanek ineslem|uwanek ineslem]] wid ixedmen axeṣṣar-agi d  Abu Hamza al-Ansari ed Abu al-Sadiq al-Ansari,.

== akemmel ==
di  17 yunyu,akken ad rren ttar wten yiserdasen n [[Ččad]]. imekwan i deg tettili buku haram
